---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { sitePath } from "../lib/paths";
---

<BaseLayout title="CPO 光引擎拆解">
  <section class="hero-panel">
    <p class="page-kicker">CPO optical engine map</p>
    <h1>CPO 光引擎拆解</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      从一个 co-packaged optical engine 的结构切入：light source、PIC、EIC、
      optical I/O 和 package integration。每个入口再回到底层材料、器件、封装、
      测试和可靠性问题。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="page-kicker">Structure</p>
      <h2>按结构进入</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="module-grid">
      <a class="module-card" href={sitePath("/components/laser-source/")}>
        <h3>CPO 光源系统</h3>
        <p>解释光在哪里产生、激光器内置还是外置，以及 CW laser、DFB/EML、ELSFP 的系统边界。</p>
      </a>

      <a class="module-card" href={sitePath("/components/pic/")}>
        <h3>PIC / optical circuit</h3>
        <p>看光在芯片里如何传播、路由、调制、复用、耦合和探测。</p>
      </a>

      <a class="module-card" href={sitePath("/components/eic/")}>
        <h3>EIC / driver and receiver</h3>
        <p>Driver、TIA、控制电路和高速电接口决定电信号如何进入或离开光引擎。</p>
      </a>

      <a class="module-card" href={sitePath("/components/optical-io/")}>
        <h3>Optical I/O / fiber coupling</h3>
        <p>把 PIC 里的光耦合到 fiber array、connector 或板级光路，决定插损和装配窗口。</p>
      </a>

      <a class="module-card" href={sitePath("/components/packaging/")}>
        <h3>Package integration</h3>
        <p>把 laser、PIC、EIC、interposer、substrate、散热路径和机械约束组织起来。</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="page-kicker">Engineering loop</p>
      <h2>制造与验证闭环</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="module-grid">
      <a class="module-card" href={sitePath("/components/manufacturing-test/")}>
        <h3>Manufacturing and test</h3>
        <p>从 wafer-level test、known-good-die 到 package-level BER，决定 demo 能否量产。</p>
      </a>

      <a class="module-card" href={sitePath("/components/reliability-operations/")}>
        <h3>Reliability and operations</h3>
        <p>老化、温漂、热循环、现场可维护性和失效定位决定 CPO 能否长期运行。</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
